## Update credential issuer metadata

To allow credentials to be refreshed manually by the user, you must add the [`credential_refresh_web_journey_url` parameter](../credential-issuer-functionality/metadata) to your credential issuer metadata. This parameter lets GOV.UK Wallet show the user a refresh button that starts a new credential issuance process.

